{"tid":1871834,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"推背圖45解 (神算吉力子)","createTime":"2020-02-09T17:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T09:12:35.000Z","uid":252506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"25b6ea5697046063055592a6fc89e9596321af91","tid":1871834,"uid":252506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T17:08:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g12mm2z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg12mm2z.jpg&h=1c5d3cf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此象中的卦，預示山（艮）被水（坎）圍困，蒙卦有被矇騙、蒙難、被險象包圍的提醒。誰被矇騙，誰在蒙難，又是什麼樣的險象？答案在坎。坎在五行中屬水，而共產黨在五行中也屬水。過去，正統文化把共產黨視為危害人類的洪水猛獸。所以共產黨到了哪裡，哪裡的人民就會被矇騙，就會蒙難，被危險環包。(呢段野有抄大紀元)<br />\n<br />\n有客西來 至東而止:<br />\n係講 瑞德西韋 從西方來到東方 (有個西字)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n木火金水 洗此大恥:<br />\n木火金水 (唔太知,係唔係五行欠土??) <br />\n洗此大恥 呢句應該是出返口氣<br />\n炎運宏開世界同:<br />\n呢句應該是肺炎散播到全世界<br />\n金烏隱匿白洋中:<br />\n金烏是指太陽,有人指係日本,亦有人指係紅太陽 (自己選擇)<br />\n而隱匿白洋中 隱匿唔洗講啦 而白洋中(好多人解做海洋,因為話D西方戰艦沉哂入海),其實 白洋可能係一個地方,Google一下,中國 湖北省,近武漢市有個湖叫白洋湖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n從此不敢稱雄長<br />\n兵氣全銷運已終<br />\n(呢2句唔洗解啦)<br />\n而個圖呢:<br />\n左手面好多人解做太陽,但係又似粒肺炎.<br />\n右手面個2條友,估計係2個大國,同心合力擊敗肺炎<br />\n神解推背圖45 完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724696b06e58efabf5369b084e8f857757769ea0","tid":1871834,"uid":252506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T17:14:40.000Z","msg":"推一下先"},{"pid":"c132bd2e8609d24c9da3178afd45a2f03ade3b58","tid":1871834,"uid":139256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T18:14:04.000Z","msg":"我睇46象比較似"},{"pid":"72bb0f1dc0ee90f8d0b25572b1c46d0971be7ee2","tid":1871834,"uid":119665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T18:37:16.000Z","msg":"蒙解作啟蒙, 要讀書,學野咁解"},{"pid":"a36d5ac5775797dd4726279838d9aafbb9f0b207","tid":1871834,"uid":348812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T18:46:04.000Z","msg":"去買莫天賜本書，佢講推背圖好準！"},{"pid":"e1fd170595d9cf3a8ea3b7b3fc3b6e4c433c639f","tid":1871834,"uid":252506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72bb0f1dc0ee90f8d0b25572b1c46d0971be7ee2","tid":1871834,"uid":119665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T18:37:16.000Z","msg":"蒙解作啟蒙, 要讀書,學野咁解"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T02:28:20.000Z","msg":"抄大紀元<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3933045076850fc73839f999a9eebcb6a96e06b","tid":1871834,"uid":272355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T23:53:10.000Z","msg":"點睇都係日本仔比美國佬炸兩粒原子彈"},{"pid":"f22f794b3e96a07ef261dc97e5533b91162ea788","tid":1871834,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T06:13:33.000Z","msg":"從來推背圖只講中國本土，唔會講其他國家"},{"pid":"5c5f659e5d883f903059b89c20d13ae338240511","tid":1871834,"uid":317257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T09:12:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}